ne\",\n   920→            \"docs\": [\n   921→              \"Deadline for VRF resolution; after this, timeout refund is available.\"\n   922→            ],\n   923→            \"type\": \"i64\"\n   924→          },\n   925→          {\n   926→            \"name\": \"vrf_request_key\",\n   927→            \"docs\": [\n   928→              \"Address of the Orao randomness PDA for VRF lookup at claim time.\"\n   929→            ],\n   930→            \"type\": \"pubkey\"\n   931→          },\n   932→          {\n   933→            \"name\": \"winning_slot\",\n   934→            \"docs\": [\n   935→              \"The winning slot index (only valid after settlement).\"\n   936→            ],\n   937→            \"type\": \"u32\"\n   938→          },\n   939→          {\n   940→            \"name\": \"winner\",\n   941→            \"docs\": [\n   942→              \"The winner's pubkey (Pubkey::default() until settled).\"\n   943→            ],\n   944→            \"type\": \"pubkey\"\n   945→          },\n   946→          {\n   947→            \"name\": \"claimed\",\n   948→            \"docs\": [\n   949→              \"Whether the payout has been claimed.\"\n   950→            ],\n   951→            \"type\": \"bool\"\n   952→          },\n   953→          {\n   954→            \"name\": \"creator\",\n   955→            \"docs\": [\n   956→              \"The creator of the round (receives rent back on close).\"\n   957→            ],\n   958→            \"type\": \"pubkey\"\n   959→          },\n   960→          {\n   961→            \"name\": \"bump\",\n   962→            \"docs\": [\n   963→              \"Bump seed for PDA derivation.\"\n   964→            ],\n   965→            \"type\": \"u8\"\n   966→          }\n   967→        ]\n   968→      }\n   969→    },\n   970→    {\n   971→      \"name\": \"LordConfig\",\n   972→      \"docs\": [\n   973→        \"Global configuration for the Lord of the RNGs program.\",\n   974→        \"PDA seeds: [b\\\"lord_config\\\"]\"\n   975→      ],\n   976→      \"type\": {\n   977→        \"kind\": \"struct\",\n   978→        \"fields\": [\n   979→          {\n   980→            \"name\": \"authority\",\n   981→            \"docs\": [\n   982→              \"Admin authority (can update config).\"\n   983→            ],\n   984→            \"type\": \"pubkey\"\n   985→          },\n   986→          {\n   987→            \"name\": \"treasury\",\n   988→            \"docs\": [\n   989→              \"Fee destination wallet.\"\n   990→            ],\n   991→            \"type\": \"pubkey\"\n   992→          },\n   993→          {\n   994→            \"name\": \"paused\",\n   995→            \"docs\": [\n   996→              \"Whether the game is paused (rejects new rounds).\"\n   997→            ],\n   998→            \"type\": \"bool\"\n   999→          },\n  1000→          {\n  1001→            \"name\": \"round_counters\",\n  1002→            \"docs\": [\n  1003→              \"Monotonically increasing round counter per tier.\",\n  1004→              \"Index corresponds to tier (0–5).\"\n  1005→            ],\n  1006→            \"type\": {\n  1007→              \"array\": [\n  1008→                \"u64\",\n  1009→                6\n  1010→              ]\n  1011→            }\n  1012→          },\n  1013→          {\n  1014→            \"name\": \"bump\",\n  1015→            \"docs\": [\n  1016→              \"Bump seed for PDA derivation.\"\n  1017→            ],\n  1018→            \"type\": \"u8\"\n  1019→          }\n  1020→        ]\n  1021→      }\n  1022→    },\n  1023→    {\n  1024→      \"name\": \"PlayerEntry\",\n  1025→      \"docs\": [\n  1026→        \"A single player's entry in a jackpot round.\"\n  1027→      ],\n  1028→      \"type\": {\n  1029→        \"kind\": \"struct\",\n  1030→        \"fields\": [\n  1031→          {\n  1032→            \"name\": \"player\",\n  1033→            \"docs\": [\n  1034→              \"Player's wallet address.\"\n  1035→            ],\n  1036→            \"type\": \"pubkey\"\n  1037→          },\n  1038→          {\n  1039→            \"name\": \"entries\",\n  1040→            \"docs\": [\n  1041→              \"Number of entries purchased (each entry = one slot on the wheel).\"\n  1042→            ],\n  1043→            \"type\": \"u32\"\n  1044→          }\n  1045→        ]\n  1046→      }\n  1047→    },\n  1048→    {\n  1049→      \"name\": \"RoundPhase\",\n  1050→      \"docs\": [\n  1051→        \"Lifecycle phase for every round/match in any game.\"\n  1052→      ],\n  1053→      \"type\": {\n  1054→        \"kind\": \"enum\",\n  1055→        \"variants\": [\n  1056→          {\n  1057→            \"name\": \"Waiting\"\n  1058→          },\n  1059→          {\n  1060→            \"name\": \"Active\"\n  1061→          },\n  1062→          {\n  1063→            \"name\": \"Locked\"\n  1064→          },\n  1065→          {\n  1066→            \"name\": \"Resolving\"\n  1067→          },\n  1068→          {\n  1069→            \"name\": \"Settled\"\n  1070→          },\n  1071→          {\n  1072→            \"name\": \"Refunded\"\n  1073→          }\n  1074→        ]\n  1075→      }\n  1076→    },\n  1077→    {\n  1078→      \"name\": \"RoundSettled\",\n  1079→      \"docs\": [\n  1080→        \"Event emitted when a round is settled via claim_payout.\"\n  1081→      ],\n  1082→      \"type\": {\n  1083→        \"kind\": \"struct\",\n  1084→        \"fields\": [\n  1085→          {\n  1086→            \"name\": \"tier\",\n  1087→            \"docs\": [\n  1088→              \"Tier index.\"\n  1089→            ],\n  1090→            \"type\": \"u8\"\n  1091→          },\n  1092→          {\n  1093→            \"name\": \"round_number\",\n  1094→            \"docs\": [\n  1095→              \"Round number.\"\n  1096→            ],\n  1097→            \"type\": \"u64\"\n  1098→          },\n  1099→          {\n  1100→            \"name\": \"winner\",\n  1101→            \"docs\": [\n  1102→              \"Winner's wallet address.\"\n  1103→            ],\n  1104→            \"type\": \"pubkey\"\n  1105→          },\n  1106→          {\n  1107→            \"name\": \"randomness\",\n  1108→            \"docs\": [\n  1109→              \"Raw VRF randomness bytes.\"\n  1110→            ],\n  1111→            \"type\": {\n  1112→              \"array\": [\n  1113→                \"u8\",\n  1114→                32\n  1115→              ]\n  1116→            }\n  1117→          },\n  1118→          {\n  1119→            \"name\": \"winning_slot\",\n  1120→            \"docs\": [\n  1121→              \"The winning slot index (0-based).\"\n  1122→            ],\n  1123→            \"type\": \"u32\"\n  1124→          },\n  1125→          {\n  1126→            \"name\": \"total_entries\",\n  1127→            \"docs\": [\n  1128→              \"Total entries in the round.\"\n  1129→            ],\n  1130→            \"type\": \"u32\"\n  1131→          },\n  1132→          {\n  1133→            \"name\": \"payout_amount\",\n  1134→            \"docs\": [\n  1135→              \"Net payout to winner (after fee).\"\n  1136→            ],\n  1137→            \"type\": \"u64\"\n  1138→          },\n  1139→          {\n  1140→            \"name\": \"fee_amount\",\n  1141→            \"docs\": [\n  1142→              \"Platform fee amount.\"\n  1143→            ],\n  1144→            \"type\": \"u64\"\n  1145→          },\n  1146→          {\n  1147→            \"name\": \"vrf_request_key\",\n  1148→            \"docs\": [\n  1149→              \"Address of the Orao VRF request PDA.\"\n  1150→            ],\n  1151→            \"type\": \"pubkey\"\n  1152→          }\n  1153→        ]\n  1154→      }\n  1155→    }\n  1156→  ]\n  1157→}"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01S6BoVZdVizC3kZTvirWjHW","session_id":"8e5d7c3d-ef66-4971-8f66-de7d7c43ed7c","uuid":"9de7409c-1e56-4473-b637-c2ae78bef77d"}
